! Basic Graph

A simple graph with colored nodes, edges, and different line styles.

<div style="height:450px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:4px;margin:8px 0;">
<$graph>
  <$node $tiddler="A" label="Node A" color="CornflowerBlue"/>
  <$node $tiddler="B" label="Node B" color="Coral"/>
  <$node $tiddler="C" label="Node C" color="MediumSeaGreen"/>
  <$node $tiddler="D" label="Node D" color="Gold"/>
  <$edge $from="A" $to="B"/>
  <$edge $from="B" $to="C"/>
  <$edge $from="C" $to="D"/>
  <$edge $from="A" $to="C" stroke="dashed"/>
  <$edge $from="B" $to="D" stroke="dotted"/>
</$graph>
</div>

